  <brief_title>Retention and Duration of Activity of SPL7013 (VivaGel®) After Vaginal Dosing.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of Local Retention and Duration of Activity of SPL7013 Following Vaginal Application of 3% SPL7013 Gel (VivaGel) in Healthy Volunteers</official_title>
